[Name] Premake
[Summary] A build script generation tool
[Description] Premake is a build script generator. It allows you to describe your project
using the Lua scripting language and then let Premake create the input files for
MS Visual Studio, GNU make, SharpDevelop, MonoDevelop, etc.
[License] GNU General Public License, version 2
[Homepage] http://premake.sourceforge.net